node.text: @msrachelhollis👇 (link in bio) We talk about loving yourself and seeing failure as success. We all need to learn to see the positive aspects of every failure in our life, to take proper care of ourselves by taking good care of our health, to sit down and process pain and grief at our own pace, and to never lose ourselves just to keep a relationship.

node.text:
Your choices are a power 💛 Comment a YES below if you love this post from @jayshettygenius ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Intention isn't something you do, but an energy you're able to call upon whenever you need. When you lead with pure intention, you become a force for good.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
This is why @jayshettygenius exists 🙏 to help you become your most intentional self, one decision at a time. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
We meet in weekly workshops and meditations every week to grow, learn, and reflect. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
I'll see you in the next @jayshettygenius workshop. Link in bio to join now! 👉 jayshettygenius.com

node.text: Insecurities manifest differently for everyone. However, when insecurities that are not dealt with become overwhelming and spin out of control, it may cause harm to yourself or those around you.

node.text:
Drop a “YES” if you’ve read Think Like A Monk👇 I can’t believe it! Think Like A Monk released 1 year ago! It’s been incredible to see so many of you resonate with this book.  The book came out at a time when I could not travel, do any events or interviews but at a time when you all told me you really needed to know about the monk mindset. Thank you for supporting me and I’m glad this book supported you! You can get the hardback and audiobook at www.thinklikeamonkbook.com (link in bio)⁠⁠
⁠⁠
I am so grateful for all the love I’ve received from all over the world! Here are some of the highlights! ⁠⁠

#1 New York Times Bestseller ⁠⁠
#1 Sunday Times Bestseller ⁠⁠
#1 Amazon Bestseller India | UK | Australia | ⁠⁠

node.text: Drop a ❤️ below if you agree👇People want your energy. They want your attention. They want you! Your presence is you. It’s your essence.
